474
00:35:24.387 --> 00:35:26.951
Het lijkt onwaarschijnlijk.

475
00:35:33.396 --> 00:35:35.396
Pip. Pip.

476
00:35:36.858 --> 00:35:38.858
Kom op, jongen.

477
00:36:25.240 --> 00:36:26.599
Pip.

478
00:36:26.699 --> 00:36:28.699
Joe, mag ik?

479
00:37:30.305 --> 00:37:32.305
Biddy, ik wil...

480
00:37:33.516 --> 00:37:35.084
Ga door.

481
00:37:35.184 --> 00:37:37.184
Pip?

482
00:37:41.399 --> 00:37:43.523
Biddy, ik wou dat ik
